videos.description: Kennedy Brooks takes the handoff and powers through the Baylor defense to score a six-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brooks muscles his way to score Oklahoma's 1st TD) 2019/12/07

videos.headline: Brooks muscles his way to score Oklahoma's 1st TD

videos.description: Charlie Brewer breaks out of the pocket for a seven-yard gain and lays a nice hit on Oklahoma defender Brendan Radley-Hiles in the process.
videos.headline: Baylor's Brewer trucks Radley-Hiles

videos.description: Jalen Hurts drops back and throws an interception to Jordan Williams, who returns it five yards to the Oklahoma 23-yard line.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hurts gets picked off by Baylor's Williams) 2019/12/07

videos.headline: Hurts gets picked off by Baylor's Williams

videos.description: Gerry Bohanon lets it fly and connects with Tyquan Thornton in the end zone to score a 33-yard Baylor touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bohanon connects with Thornton on deep 33-yard TD pass) 2019/12/07

videos.headline: Bohanon connects with Thornton on deep 33-yard TD pass

videos.description: Baylor head coach Matt Rhule says quarterback Charlie Brewer is being held out of the second half for health reasons after suffering a jarring hit in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Brewer ruled out for rest of Big 12 title game) 2019/12/07

videos.headline: Brewer ruled out for rest of Big 12 title game

videos.description: Jalen Hurts completes a pass to Nick Basquine to score an 18-yard touchdown, giving Oklahoma a 20-13 lead over Baylor.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Oklahoma's Basquine makes the grab for 18-yard TD) 2019/12/07

videos.headline: Oklahoma's Basquine makes the grab for 18-yard TD

videos.description: Trestan Ebner leaps up to snag a catch and takes off for an 81-yard touchdown to cut into Oklahoma's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ebner turns on the jets for an 81-yard TD) 2019/12/7

videos.headline: Ebner turns on the jets for an 81-yard TD

videos.description: Baylor QB Charlie Brewer suffers a hit to the head and gets up wobbly after being tackled early in the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Baylor's Brewer hits his head on the ground after getting tackled) 2019/12/7

videos.headline: Brewer hits his head on the ground after getting tackled

videos.description: Rhamondre Stevenson takes the handoff and navigates his way to the end zone for a five-yard Oklahoma touchdown, giving the Sooners a 30-23 lead over Baylor in overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Oklahoma's Stevenson scores short TD in OT for the lead) 2019/12/07

videos.headline: Oklahoma's Stevenson scores short TD in OT

videos.description: Jacob Zeno collapses under the pressure of the Oklahoma defense and throws an incomplete pass on fourth-and-long as the Sooners seal their Big 12 championship victory.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Oklahoma makes big stop on 4th down to seal Big 12 championship) 2019/12/07

videos.headline: Oklahoma makes big stop on 4th down to seal Big 12 championship

videos.description: Jalen Hurts reacts to Oklahoma's overtime victory vs. Baylor in the Big 12 Championship game.
videos.headline: Hurts: 'Our story ain't over'
